{{vgname|羽生名人之趣味将棋|ja=羽生名人のおもしろ将棋}}是一款由[[Access|Access]]制作，[[多美_(公司)|Tomy]]发行的将棋类[[游戏|游戏]]。本游戏于1995年3月31日在日本地区[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]发行。<ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamefaqs.com/snes/571263-habu-meijin-no-omoshiro-shogi/data| title = Release information| publisher = [[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]| date = | accessdate = 2015-09-26| archive-date = 2015-12-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151226044326/http://www.gamefaqs.com/snes/571263-habu-meijin-no-omoshiro-shogi/data| dead-url = no}}</ref>

本游戏由[[羽生善治|羽生善治]]监制。

[[Fami通|Fami通]]对本游戏的评分为25/40分。<ref>NEW GAMES CROSS REVIEW: 羽生名人のおもしろ将棋. Weekly Famicom Tsūshin. No.329. Pg.31. 7 April 1995.</ref>

